# Keep the Docker build context small and reproducible. Note: the Gradle wrapper
# directory `gradle/` is NOT excluded — the build needs gradle-wrapper.jar. The
# component-tests/ module is kept because settings.gradle.kts includes it (Gradle
# requires the project directory to exist), but its build output is dropped below.
.git/
.gradle/
**/build/
.idea/
.claude/
*.iml
HELP.md
